# HANZO Buyer UI

When building or editing buyer views, follow `HANZO_BUYER_SPEC.md` for design system and layout.

## Security (never violate)

- **Factory contact data:** Do not render `phone`, `email`, `wechat`, `whatsapp`, or `direct_contact`. Controllers must call `FactoryPrivacy::forBuyer($factory)` before passing to views.
- **hanzo_margin:** Never expose in any buyer-facing view or API response.
- Use `@csrf` in all forms. Blade `{{ }}` escapes output by default.

## Design tokens

- Dark theme: `--hz-navy`, `--hz-navy-2`, `--hz-navy-3` (backgrounds)
- Accent: `--hz-gold`, `--hz-gold-light` (CTAs, prices)
- Success: `--hz-verified`. Danger: `--hz-danger`
- Borders: `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`
- Typography: Plus Jakarta Sans / DM Sans, base 14px

## Component patterns

- Cards: `background: var(--hz-navy-2)`, `border-radius: 12px`, 1px border
- Primary button: gold bg, dark text, font-weight 600
- Ghost button: transparent, gold border and text
- No box shadows; use borders for depth
